Date: Wed, 15 Apr 2009 11:21:26 +0800
Subject: [PATCH] ENGR00111242-4-MX3X/27 Enable the CONFIG_MMC_UNSAFE_RESUME option

Enable the CONFIG_MMC_UNSAFE_RESUME option, to support
the mmc/sd rootfs.

Signed-off-by: Richard Zhu <r65037@freescale.com>
---
 arch/arm/configs/imx27ads_defconfig     |    2 +-
 arch/arm/configs/imx31_3stack_defconfig |    2 +-
 arch/arm/configs/imx31ads_defconfig     |    2 +-
 arch/arm/configs/imx35_3stack_defconfig |    2 +-
 arch/arm/configs/imx37_3stack_defconfig |    2 +-
 5 files changed, 5 insertions(+), 5 deletions(-)

diff --git a/arch/arm/configs/imx27ads_defconfig b/arch/arm/configs/imx27ads_defconfig
index 153dd43..7b2f601 100644
--- a/arch/arm/configs/imx27ads_defconfig
+++ b/arch/arm/configs/imx27ads_defconfig
@@ -1232,7 +1232,7 @@ CONFIG_USB_G_SERIAL=m
 # CONFIG_USB_G_PRINTER is not set
 CONFIG_MMC=y
 # CONFIG_MMC_DEBUG is not set
-# CONFIG_MMC_UNSAFE_RESUME is not set
+CONFIG_MMC_UNSAFE_RESUME=y
 
